hanges, no verification needed.\n   273→\n   274→## Phase 2 Refinement Summary (2026-02-26)\n   275→\n   276→Phase 2 added 19 checklist items to address gaps identified after the 004 shared-infrastructure rewrite. All 19 items completed across iterations 10-20:\n   277→\n   278→| Category | Items | Iterations |\n   279→|----------|-------|------------|\n   280→| Data consistency (tier rename + amounts) | 2 | 10-11 |\n   281→| Claimable matches (G-1) | 2 | 12-13 |\n   282→| Fairness verification (FR-5) | 4 | 14-17 |\n   283→| Quick rematch (FR-7.6) | 1 | 18 |\n   284→| Validation & cleanup | 4 | 19-21 |\n   285→\n   286→Architecture changes from 004 rewrite:\n   287→- **VRF**: MagicBlock Ephemeral VRF → Orao VRF (shared vrf_orao module)\n   288→- **Flow**: 4-tx (create→join→resolve→claim) → 3-tx (create→join(+VRF)→claim(+settle))\n   289→- **resolve_match**: Deleted. Winner derivation moved to claim_payout (reads Orao randomness at claim time).\n   290→- **Shared crate**: Expanded with lifecycle, escrow, timeout, pause, vrf_orao, commit_reveal, cpi modules.\n   291→- **Tests**: 30 → 31 bankrun tests (added timeout_cancel + lifecycle tests, removed resolve_match tests).\n   292→\n   293→## Iteration 21 — 2026-02-26T08:54:11Z — OK\n   294→- **Log**: iteration-021.log\n   295→\n   296→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f244d339-d9e0-4d86-97fb-bcb906c0be01","uuid":"8c30a705-2b3f-4118-8992-c38b952be2e3","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/001-coinflip/history.md","content":"# Implementation History — 001-coinflip\n\nIteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\nattempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\nof every iteration to understand prior context.\n\n---\n\n## Iteration 0 — 2026-02-17T14:42:30Z — BLOCKED\n- **Blocker**: Spec is still Draft. Run '/refine 001-coinflip' to break down the checklist.\n\n## Iteration 1 — 2026-02-17 — DONE\n- **Item**: Alig