{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01YbfrVz4zgSc3heh6Np4AHd","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have comprehensive information. Let me create a summary report:\n\n## Visual Testing Setup Summary\n\nI've thoroughly explored the visual testing infrastructure in this project. Here's what I found:\n\n### 1. **Visual Test Files Location**\n- **Visual test files**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/`\n  - `routes.spec.ts` - Tests full-page screenshots of all routes (12 routes covered)\n  - `states.spec.ts` - Tests different UI states (wallet connected/disconnected variations)\n- **Real mode tests**: `e2e/real/startup.spec.ts` - Tests without determinism (real wallet mode)\n- **Test fixtures**: `e2e/fixtures.ts` - Shared test setup with determinism controls\n\n### 2. **Visual Baselines Storage**\n- **Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/`\n- **Structure**: Nested by test file:\n  - `__snapshots__/visual/routes.spec.ts/` - 12 PNG baselines (home.png, coinflip.png, crash.png, etc.)\n  - `__snapshots__/visual/states.spec.ts/` - 5 PNG baselines (home-disconnected.png, home-connected.png, etc.)\n- **Size**: ~20MB total for all baselines\n- **Format**: PNG images with configurable diff ratio (0.015 max diff pixel ratio in config)\n\n### 3. **Test Framework: Playwright**\n- **Framework**: **Playwright v1.58.2** (`@playwright/test`)\n- **Configuration Files**:\n  - `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.config.ts` - Main config for mock mode tests\n  - `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.real.config.ts` - Config for real wallet mode tests\n- **Snapshot Strategy**: Custom path template `{testDir}/__snapshots__/{testFilePath}/{arg}{ext}`\n- **Snapshot Assertion Method**: `expect(page).toHaveScreenshot()`\n\n### 4. **NPM Scripts for Visual Tests**\n\nRoot level (`sources/rng-utopia/package.json`):\n```json\n\"test:visual\": \"turbo run test:visual\"\n```\n\nPlatform app level (`apps/platform/package.json`):\n```json\n\"test:visual\": \"playwright test\",\n\"test:visual:update\": \"playwright test --update-snapshots\"\n```\n\n### 5. **Playwright Configuration Details**\n\n**Mock Mode (playwright.config.ts)**:\n- Test directory: `./e2e`\n- Base URL: `http://localhost:3000`\n- Viewport: 1280x1080 (Desktop Chrome)\n- Snapshot diff tolerance: `maxDiffPixelRatio: 0.015` (1.5%)\n- Web server: Runs with `VITE_MOCK_MODE: \"true\"`\n- Snapshot path template: `{testDir}/__snapshots__/{testFilePath}/{arg}{ext}`\n- Workers: 1 (serial execution)\n\n**Real Mode (playwright.real.config.ts)**:\n- Test directory: `./e2e` (filters `real/**/*.spec.ts`)\n- Base URL: `http://localhost:3001`\n- Web server: Runs with `VITE_MOCK_MODE: \"false\"` and `VITE_RPC_URL: \"https://api.devnet.solana.com\"`\n\n### 6. **Determinism & Test Stabilization**\n\nThe `fixtures.ts` file implements a sophisticated `stablePage` fixture that ensures visual test determinism:\n\n- **Seeded PRNG**: Uses Mulberry32 with seed 42 for deterministic `Math.random()`\n- **Frozen Time**: Locks `Date.now()` to `2026-01-01T00:00:00Z` (1767225600000 ms)\n- **Crypto Determinism**: Seeds `crypto.getRandomValues()` so wallet keypair generation is deterministic\n- **Animation Freezing**: Injects CSS to disable all CSS/SVG animations and transitions\n- **SVG SMIL Pausing**: Pauses SVG SMIL animations via JavaScript\n- **Network Idle Waiting**: Overrides `goto()` to wait for `networkidle` and fonts to load\n- **Console Error Catching**: Collects and fails test if any console errors occur\n\n### 7. **Test Coverage**\n\n**Route baselines** (12 pages):\n- home, coinflip, lord-of-rngs, close-call, crash, game-of-trades, profile, quests, loot, fairness, leaderboard, 404\n\n**State variations** (5 tests):\n- home-disconnected, home-connected, profile-connected, coinflip-disconnected, coinflip-connected\n\n### Key Files Summary\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `/apps/platform/playwright.config.ts` | Main visual test config for mock mode |\n| `/apps/platform/playwright.real.config.ts` | Config for real wallet integration tests |\n| `/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts` | Shared test fixture with determinism setup |\n| `/apps/platform/e2e/visual/routes.spec.ts` | Route baseline tests |\n| `/apps/platform/e2e/visual/states.spec.ts` | State variation tests |\n| `/apps/platform/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/` | PNG baseline storage (~20MB) |\n| `/apps/platform/e2e/real/startup.spec.ts` | Real mode startup tests |"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a98587a72213e2b0d (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 42049\ntool_uses: 29\nduration_ms: 72738</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f244d339-d9e0-4d86-97fb-bcb906c0be01","uuid":"7d3a75ec-5f10-4332-8fd2-fcf678ad131b","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Find and describe the visual testing setup in this project. I need to understand:\n\n1. Where are visual test files? Look for files with patterns like `*.visual.*`, `*.screenshot.*`, `*.spec.ts` that relate to visual/screenshot tests in `sources/rng-utopia/`\n2. Where are visual baselines stored? Look for directories like `__snapshots__`, `screenshots`, `baselines`, `visual-baselines` etc.\n3. What test framework is used for visual tests? (Playwright? Storybook?)\n4. What npm scripts exist for visual tests? Check `package.json` files for `test:visual` or similar\n5. Is there a playwright config? Look for `playwright.config.*` files\n\nSearch broadly in `sources/rng-utopia/` and also check the root `/workspaces/rng-utopia/`.\n\nBe thorough - check multiple patterns and locations.","agentId":"a98587a72213e2b0d","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have comprehensive information. Let me create a summary report:\n\n## Visual Testing Setup Summary\n\nI've thoroughly explored the visual testi