{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01N87DvYKpFo56Qu7VEGqyfk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01SCyQRdi1JTf4yNTmfpLtmU","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/001-coinflip/spec.md","old_string":"- [ ] [test] Update visual baselines for coinflip pages. Run `pnpm test:visual` to identify failures from tier name/amount changes. Then `pnpm test:visual:update` to regenerate. **Before committing**: read old baseline and new screenshot for each changed page (use Read tool on PNG files). Evaluate:\n  - **PASS** (changes clearly match spec intent, only expected areas changed) → commit updated baselines\n  - **REVIEW** (changes look plausible but unexpected areas also changed, or uncertain) → do NOT commit baselines. Save the diff images from `test-results/` to `docs/specs/001-coinflip/visual-review/`, describe concerns in `history.md`, output `<blocker>Visual review needed: [describe what looks off]</blocker>`\n  - **FAIL** (layout broken, elements missing, clearly wrong) → fix the code, do NOT update baselines","new_string":"- [x] [test] Update visual baselines for coinflip pages. Run `pnpm test:visual` to identify failures from tier name/amount changes. Then `pnpm test:visual:update` to regenerate. **Before committing**: read old baseline and new screenshot for each changed page (use Read tool on PNG files). Evaluate:\n  - **PASS** (changes clearly match spec intent, only expected areas changed) → commit updated baselines\n  - **REVIEW** (changes look plausible but unexpected areas also changed, or uncertain) → do NOT commit baselines. Save the diff images from `test-results/` to `docs/specs/001-coinflip/visual-review/`, describe concerns in `history.md`, output `<blocker>Visual review needed: [describe what looks off]</blocker>`\n  - **FAIL** (layout broken, elements missing, clearly wrong) → fix the code, do NOT update baselines\n  (done: iterat